<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer1363640099434176269">Henning Mankell was an internationally known Swedish crime writer, children&apos;s author and playwright. He was best known for his literary character Kurt Wallander.<br/><br/>Mankell split his time between Sweden and Mozambique. He was married to Eva Bergman, Swedish director and daughter of Ingmar Bergman.</span>
  <span id="freeText1363640099434176269" style="display:none">Henning Mankell was an internationally known Swedish crime writer, children's author and playwright. He was best known for his literary character Kurt Wallander.<br /><br />Mankell split his time between Sweden and Mozambique. He was married to Eva Bergman, Swedish director and daughter of Ingmar Bergman.</span>
